        dc:description           "Fig. 9. — Typical leaves of the Leonardoxa africana complex, all drawn at same scale. Bar = 10 cm. A, L. africana subsp. gracilicaulis; B, L. africana subsp. rumpiensis; C, L. africana subsp. letouzeyi; D, L. africana subsp. africana." ;
